body:
Initial PEP-484 type stub for pure Python mode, including mypy based type checking test.

Supersedes #1964.

commit.message: Add Shadow.pyi from typeshed's pull request

Add FusedType to Shadow.pyi

* `FusedType` for the PEP484's stub file

Add mypy test capability to PureDoctestTestCase

* run mypy against test modules tagged with `mypy`

WIP: Add mypy tag to pure_py3.py

* Add `mypy` as a tag to the `pure_py3.py` test module.
* Add type hint for MyStruct2 in pure_py3 test, because MyStruct2 is of type
  `cython.typedef` instead of `cython.StructType`, so one needs to explicitly
  provide its type.
Merge branch 'annotation_pyi_test' of https://github.com/smartsammler/cython into mypy
Install mypy only in travis tests, not generally in test dependencies, as it requires Py3.
Add some missing types to Shadow.pyi and comment out incomplete ones.

title: [WIP] Type annotation pyi file and tests (II)
